Titolo: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire (video game)

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire is a 2005 action-adventure video game published by Electronic Arts. It is based on the 2005 film of the same name. The game was developed by three teams, EA UK, Magic Pockets, and EA Fusion UK, and was published by Electronic Arts.
The game was released for Game Boy Advance, GameCube, Microsoft Windows, Nintendo DS, PlayStation 2, Xbox, and PlayStation Portable. It received mixed reviews from critics, with reviewers enjoying the scope of the spells and gameplay, but being less impressed by the short length, and the lack of free roaming components found in previous installments.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
